There are three ways to win:
#1: BUY CHEERWINE, UPLOAD RECEIPT 
#2: POST USING #CHEERWINESUMMER 
#3: ENTER BONUS CODE SUMMERBABE 

Full contest rules and prize details can be found at cheerwine.com/contest. Good luck!! #Cheerwine #UniquelySouthern #CheerwineSummer #ad
